my-express-app/
│
├── config/
│   ├── db.js               # Sequelize connection
│   └── config.js           # App-wide configs (PORT, JWT_SECRET if needed)
│
├── controllers/
│   ├── authController.js   # Login, Register, Logout logic
│   ├── userController.js   # Users CRUD logic
│   ├── productController.js# Products CRUD logic
│   ├── categoryController.js # Categories CRUD logic
│   └── orderController.js  # Orders CRUD logic
│
├── models/
│   ├── User.js             # Sequelize User model
│   ├── Product.js          # Sequelize Product model
│   ├── Category.js         # Sequelize Category model
│   └── Order.js            # Sequelize Order model
│
├── routes/
│   ├── authRoutes.js       # /auth/login, /auth/register, /auth/logout
│   ├── userRoutes.js       # /users CRUD routes (session-protected)
│   ├── productRoutes.js    # /products CRUD routes (session-protected)
│   ├── categoryRoutes.js   # /categories CRUD routes (session-protected)
│   └── orderRoutes.js      # /orders CRUD routes (session-protected)
│
├── views/
│   ├── layouts/
│   │    ├── main.ejs       # Dashboard layout (header, sidebar, footer)
│   │    └── auth.ejs       # Auth pages layout
│   ├── auth/
│   │    ├── login.ejs
│   │    └── register.ejs
│   ├── dashboard/
│   │    └── index.ejs      # Dashboard home page
│   ├── partials/
│   │    ├── header.ejs
│   │    ├── sidebar.ejs
│   │    └── footer.ejs
│   ├── users/
│   │    ├── index.ejs      # User list
│   │    ├── add.ejs        # Add user form
│   │    └── edit.ejs       # Edit user form
│   ├── products/
│   │    ├── index.ejs
│   │    ├── add.ejs
│   │    └── edit.ejs
│   ├── categories/
│   │    ├── index.ejs
│   │    ├── add.ejs
│   │    └── edit.ejs
│   └── orders/
│        ├── index.ejs
│        ├── add.ejs
│        └── edit.ejs
│
├── middleware/
│   ├── authMiddleware.js   # Session-protect routes (redirect if not logged in)
│   └── errorMiddleware.js  # Optional error handling middleware
│
├── utils/
│   └── fileUpload.js       # File upload helpers
│
├── uploads/                # Uploaded files (images)
│
├── server.js               # Express app entry point
└── package.json


➡️ Register:

http://localhost:5000/auth/register

➡️ Login:

http://localhost:5000/auth/login

➡️ After Login → Redirect to Dashboard:

http://localhost:5000/dashboard

http://localhost:5000/api/users
http://localhost:5000/api/products


=> API Endpoints

1. Auth APIs

    POST /api/auth/register → User registration

    POST /api/auth/login → User login

    GET /api/auth/me → Get logged-in user profile

2. User APIs

    GET /api/users/ → List users (admin only)

    GET /api/users/:id → Get user detail

    PUT /api/users/:id → Update user

    DELETE /api/users/:id → Delete user

3. Category APIs

    GET /api/categories/ → List categories

    POST /api/categories/ → Add category (admin only)

    PUT /api/categories/:id → Update category (admin only)

    DELETE /api/categories/:id → Delete category (admin only)

4. Product APIs

    GET /api/products/ → List products

    GET /api/products/:id → Get product details

    POST /api/products/ → Add product (admin only)

    PUT /api/products/:id → Update product (admin only)

    DELETE /api/products/:id → Delete product (admin only)

5. Order APIs

    GET /api/orders/ → List all orders (admin only)

    GET /api/orders/:id → Get order details

    POST /api/orders/ → Place new order

    PUT /api/orders/:id → Update order status (admin only)

    DELETE /api/orders/:id → Cancel order



    Suggested Packages (Node.js)

    mkdir ecommerce-app
    cd ecommerce-app
    npm init -y
    npm install express mysql2 sequelize dotenv bcryptjs jsonwebtoken multer cors
    npm install --save-dev nodemon

    "scripts": {
        "start": "node server.js",
        "dev": "nodemon server.js"
    }

    express → Web framework

    mysql2 / sequelize → MySQL ORM

    dotenv → Environment variables

    bcryptjs → Password hashing

    jsonwebtoken → JWT authentication

    multer → File uploads (product images)

    cors → Enable cross-origin requests